{"article_id":"sp9aYhIsnSwpfqKK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"' I will speak","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"as long","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"as it takes ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"until the alarm is sounded from coast to coast , '","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Paul said .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Rand Paul pulls plug on nearly 13-hour filibuster","depth":2},{"id":6,"text":"Kentucky Sen. Rand Paul staged the longest talking filibuster in recent Senate memory from Wednesday into early Thursday ,","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"railing with his colleagues for more than 12 hours against what they called the danger of drone strikes to U.S. citizens on American soil .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"In seizing control of the Senate ,","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"a bloc of conservatives","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"led by the libertarian Paul","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"successfully pushed a potential vote","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to confirm President Barack Obama ' s nominee","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"to run the CIA","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"off the day ' s agenda .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Paul began speaking at 11:47 a.m. on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"and finally yielded the floor at about 12:39 a.m. Thursday ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"having stayed inside the Senate chamber and on his feet for that entire time .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" I would try to go another 12 hours","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"and try to break Strom Thurmond ' s record ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"but there are some limits to filibustering","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and I am going to have to go take care of one of those here , \"","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Paul said .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Immediately after he finished ,","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"Majority Whip Dick Durbin of Illinois introduced a motion","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"to end debate on the nomination of John Brennan","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"to run the CIA .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Speaking to reporters afterward ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Paul said","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"he hadn ' t done much preparation for what turned into a rare marathon talkfest .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"\" Well the weird thing is that we did n't really have a plan , \"","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"\" We showed up this morning","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"thinking","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"[ the Brennan ] debate was going to be tomorrow ...","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"I had n't planned on it .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"I did n't wear my most comfortable shoes or anything .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"I would have worn different shoes . ''","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"He did use some strategy :","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` I went to the candy drawer a lot of times ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and I did n't drink much water ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"so I need some water , \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"A spokeswoman said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Paul had not taken a steam bath","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"as Thurmond had for his record-setting 24-hour filibuster .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" I 'm very tired , \"","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"he acknowledged .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"\" My legs hurt ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"my feet hurt ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"everything hurts . ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"Paul 's gambit initially surprised the Senate ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"many members of which had been prepared to vote","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"to confirm Brennan","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to take over the spy agency earlier Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"as the day wore on ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"several of Paul 's colleagues","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"- as well as one Democrat -","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"joined him","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"to attack the Obama administration for its refusal","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"to positively rule out the use of drones against Americans in the U.S.","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"or to disclose more information about drones .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"By nightfall , Paul ' s effort had gained the support of more of his colleagues ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"including Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"They joined him on the floor","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"and used up chunks of time with quotes from Ronald Reagan , Shakespeare , and in the case of Florida Sen. Marco Rubio , \" The Godfather \" and rapper Jay-Z .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"Just short of the 12-hour mark , Republican National Committee Chairman Reince Priebus called via Twitter for \" all Republican US senators \" to join the filibuster .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"So , Sen. Ron Johnson of Wisconsin gave a speech as much about the dysfunctional Senate and the dangers of the national debt as about drone policy .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Sen. Tim Scott of South Carolina said","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that the essential issue of liberty shouldn ' t divide the political parties .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake of Arizona told Paul","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"\" the question","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"you ' ve asked","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"is totally right and proper. \"","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"And so on .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":151,"left":81,"right":150,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":81,"left":80,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":2,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":97,"right":149,"relation":"elabora